  "texts": [
    "This is even more evident in further prompts.",
    "When questioned about the units of measurement used in network flows, the LLM failed to provide a coherent answer.",
    "When provided with a malformed NetFlow, the LLM was unable to determine its soundness.",
    "Additionally, the LLM failed to explain a SYN flood attack, a straightforward task for signature-based detectors like Cisco Snort.",
    "Computational ComplexityThe feasibility of using LLMs for NIDS not only relies on detection performance but as importantly on inference time."
